song_name: Everything Works Out In The End

version_description: This is the acoustic version Capo is on 2 (although in the video he has his guitar tuned half step down so his capo is on 3).

Hi, this tab has the chords at the right times and correct lyrics. Also, the Chords for the Instrumental breaks and outro have been added. Much easier to play along for novice guitar players (because of the timing of the chords).
Because it's correct, compared to the others

The song is mostly a capella so this is a try to put matching chords to the song. The song is in G# so play it using these chords and capo on the 1st fret. Hope you like it and please ad improvements.
More accurate sounding chords to play along with the song.
This is my first chord submission, hope this will be better I love this song so much.
My version does not require a capo and is in standard tuning, unlike the other versions of this song.
Capo 4th fret, chord shapes are in the key of G (original key: B major)... Transcribed from Kodaline's official lyric video: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=lVzwcNv3568.
